      • createNewInstance

        public ProcessDefinitionBuilder createNewInstance​(String name,
                                                  String version)
        Initiates the building of a new DesignProcessDefinition with the given name and version. This method is the entry point of this builder. It must be called before any other method. The DesignProcessDefinition building will be completed when the method done() or getProcess() is called.
        Parameters:
        name - the process name
        version - the process version
        Returns:
        this builder. Its ID is ZERO, as it is not deployed yet.
